{"title": "Conda 命令 - 个人文章 ", "index": "python", "content": "conda命令介绍\nconda 是一个跨平台的包管理器也是一个环境管理器;conda的优势是可以创建运行不同python版本的开发环境.\n1.检查conda是否安装\n conda --version / conda -V\n2.获取帮助\nconda -h\nconda command -h\n3.包升级\n conda update packageName\n\n4.创建并激活一个环境\n conda create -n(--name) environMentName python=2 packageNames\n conda create -n tvkenv python=2 tvk \n (在一个新的环境中创建众多包)\n\n 激活环境\n   Linux，OS X: source activate vtkenv\n   Windows：activate vtkenv\n\n 退出环境\n   Linux，OS X: source deactivate\n   Windows: deactivate\n5.列出所有(信息或者环境）\n conda info -e (--envs)所有环境\n conda info -a (--all) 所有信息\n6.复制一个环境\n conda create -n newvtkenv --clone vtkevn\n7.删除一个环境\n conda remove -n vtkenv --all\n8.查看特定环境安装包\n conda list -n vtkenv (没有在当前环境的情况)\n conda list (处在当前环境)\n9.特定环境安装包\n conda install -n customenv beautifulsoup4 (没有在当前环境的情况)\n conda install beautifulsoup4 (处在当前环境)\n //网速不好的情况下可以先把包下载到本地然后本地安装\n (1)Downloading the package(s) (and its necessary dependencies)   directly from the Continuum Repo\n (2)And installing the tar.bz2 file using conda install \n\n参考链接:http://seanlaw.github.io/2015...http://blog.sciencenet.cn/blo...\n10.查找包\n conda search packageName\n conda search -f(--full-name) packageName (Only search for full name)\n\n11.移除特定环境的包\n conda remove packageName(当前环境下)\n conda remove -n envName packageName(特定环境下某个包)\n conda remove -n envName -all (删除环境 移除所有的包)\n参考内容:conda 命令行手册http://www.cnblogs.com/harvey...https://conda.io/docs/test-dr...\n\n                ", "mainLikeNum": ["0 "], "mainBookmarkNum": "1"}